==Introduction==
大型艦用パッシブソナー兵装です。
九三式水中聴音機の捕音機を増強した大型グレードアップバージョンで、大和型戦艦のバルバス・バウ付近にも装備されました。
専門の人員も配置して水面下の音を収集、敵潜などの早期発見に努めます。

''A Passive SONAR system for large ships.
''An upgrade from the [[Type 93 Passive SONAR]], with a larger sound collector, it was equipped on [[:Category:Yamato_Class|Yamato-class]] ships within their bulbous bow.
''The IJN had specialized personnel constantly listening on the machine, trying to quickly recognize any enemy submarines.

==Notes==
;Unbuildable.
:Ships receive a 15% ASW synergy bonus when this is used together with a [[:Category:Depth Charge Projectors|depth charge projector]] or [[:Category:Depth Charges|depth charge]]; and a 43% bonus when all three types are used (must be on the same ship). The 43% bonus does not apply when used together with a [[Category:Special Depth Charge Projectors|special DCP]].
:February 2015 Ranking Reward.
:Possible reward from [[Quests#B124|quest B124]].

